name: Rhino_85% (iOS13)
author: Alex (@Alexman1979)
description:
85% size. Install 'Rhino' for normal character size.

Only compatible on iOS13. iOS14 users please download the package marked “iOS14”.

Installed to: /Library/Themes/[fontname].theme/

Apply with theming engines e.g. SnowBoard. Package name = Fonts.

Need help? Link to tutorials in my pinned tweet
